                "answer_en": "Hello, Jim. This is Peter.\nI have some bad news.\n\nI DON'T think I can make it to the performance tonight.\nI am very sick right now.\n\nWhat do you want to do?\nWhy DON'T we go next time?\nHow about we go next week?\nOr, maybe we could go another time.\n\nWhat do you think? I’m fine with whatever you decide.\nCall me back when you get this. Thanks."
