                "answer_ko": "[음식 때문에 고생한 경험 or 술에 취한 경험]\n나는 해변에서 휴가동안 상한 음식을 먹은 것이 기억에 납니다.\n\n나는 식중독에 걸렸고 그것은 매우 나빴습니다.\n나는 속이 뒤집혔습니다.\n나는 화장실에 다시 또 다시 갔습니다. 나는 설사를 했기 때문에\n나는 나아지기 위해 조금의 약을 먹었습니다.\n나는 안에 머물고 많은 휴식을 취해야 했습니다.\n\n그 이후로, 나는 더 조심하려고 노력했습니다.",
                "question_en": "That’s the end of the situation.\nWas there a time when you couldn't make to a trip to the beach because of the bad weather?\nWhat was the weather like and what was the alternative to the situation?",
                "answer_en": "[음식 때문에 고생한 경험 or 술에 취한 경험]\nI remember eating something that went bad during a vacation at the beach.\n\nI got food poisoning and it was pretty bad.\nI had an upset stomach.\nI went to the bathroom again and again because I had the runs.\nI took some medicine to get better.\nI had to stay inside and get a lot of rest.\n\nSince then, I try to be more careful."
